&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Key Holder to help lead the way at our &lt;strong&gt;Nashville&lt;/strong&gt; store! This role is perfect for someone who thrives in a team environment, loves engaging with guests, and is passionate about sharing Little Words Project’s mission. As a Key Holder, you’ll play a huge role in bringing our brand story to life—helping guests find the perfect bracelet, guiding them through our bead-your-own experience, and supporting the team to create a welcoming, inspiring space.&lt;/p&gt;
